{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"68fceda7c2","title":"关于监督改造坏分子李凤英的制度","origin":"根据网络材料打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"67abcfa935","index":0,"year":1966,"month":7,"day":28,"articleId":"68fceda7c2"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"83550e8243","name":"山西省五台县天和公社东天和大队"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"18e927a6e8","type":"title","text":"关于监督改造坏分子李凤英的制度","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68fceda7c2"},{"id":"f27f8425ef","type":"authors","text":"山西省五台县天和公社东天和大队","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68fceda7c2"},{"id":"6b0671e021","type":"paragraph","text":"为了巩固无产阶级专政，确保社会主义建设顺利进行，我大队特制定如下制度，对李凤英进行监督改造。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68fceda7c2"},{"id":"2a91f62e52","type":"paragraph","text":"1、监督改造对象每月必须出勤20天，全年投工120个，每月积肥10担，每三天扫街一次。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68fceda7c2"},{"id":"7d540f25d6","type":"paragraph","text":"2、必须保证劳动质量，按时完成各项任务。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68fceda7c2"},{"id":"188c268f2b","type":"paragraph","text":"3、坚决不能让其在要害部门劳动，不让其进行单独流动性的工作。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68fceda7c2"},{"id":"1b1ee6ae80","type":"paragraph","text":"4、监督改造对象如有来客，必须立即向治保委员会申请登记。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68fceda7c2"},{"id":"a9573c500d","type":"paragraph","text":"5、不经治保主任批准不得任意外出，要严格请假销假制度，只许规规矩矩，不许乱说乱动。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68fceda7c2"},{"id":"d857c1c5f1","type":"paragraph","text":"6、针对其思想情况，采取个别谈话的形式，每半月向其进行一次守法教育、政策教育和前途教育，主要内容是讲主席著作和形势。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68fceda7c2"},{"id":"51029a7fe1","type":"paragraph","text":"7、责令其写出监督改造保证书。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68fceda7c2"},{"id":"4e04b981bc","type":"paragraph","text":"8、监督改造对象必须每半月向治保主任口头汇报一次思想改造情况，每月书面汇报一次。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68fceda7c2"},{"id":"49cb2145cb","type":"paragraph","text":"9、治保委员会一月向党支部汇报一次改造情况。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68fceda7c2"},{"id":"7179fd5480","type":"paragraph","text":"10、每年秋后进行一次评审，表现好，给予鼓励；表现一般，加强工作；表现坏，及时报公安局处理。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68fceda7c2"},{"id":"1fcf88ac4d","type":"paragraph","text":"为保证制度有效执行，由三人组成包夹小组……","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68fceda7c2"},{"id":"5b3a5b7287","type":"paragraph","text":"本制度从一九六六年七月二十八日起开始执行。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68fceda7c2"},{"id":"e064eab3c6","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68fceda7c2"},{"id":"e7a1fb91cb","type":"paragraph","text":" 1966.7.28","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68fceda7c2"},{"id":"f6707dd4ab","type":"appellation","text":"附:","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68fceda7c2"},{"id":"6db70291ae","type":"subtitle","text":"坏分子李凤英的《接受监督改造保证书","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68fceda7c2"},{"id":"1b9d27f64d","type":"paragraph","text":"我站在反动的立场上，对社会主义极端仇视，进行了一系列的牛鬼蛇神活动，对人民作下了罪恶事实。经过无产阶级文化大革命，我要痛改自己的错误，重新做人，为此，定出下列保证，监督和检查自己：","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68fceda7c2"},{"id":"1e021511ab","type":"paragraph","text":"一、在劳动中改造自己，保证每月出勤20天，全年投工120个，每月积肥10担，每三天扫一次街。","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68fceda7c2"},{"id":"1a7e6fd054","type":"paragraph","text":"二、保证按时、按质量地完成党交给自己的各项生产任务。","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68fceda7c2"},{"id":"fdc07fa881","type":"paragraph","text":"三、保证不随便外出，如有事，要向治保主任请假，批准再走，一定坚持销假制度。我一定要规规矩矩，不乱说乱动。","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68fceda7c2"},{"id":"91474aa058","type":"paragraph","text":"四、保证我家里来了客人时，立即向治保委员会申请登记。","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68fceda7c2"},{"id":"89b94e97ed","type":"paragraph","text":"五、抽一切可以利用的时间，积极地学习毛主席著作，让识字的人给我讲，多请别人给我读毛著。","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68fceda7c2"},{"id":"45b048e007","type":"paragraph","text":"六、每半月口头汇报治保主任，谈自己思想改造情况，每月书面汇报一次。","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68fceda7c2"},{"id":"fc819d7a82","type":"paragraph","text":"七、要坚持集体生产劳动，决不能单独行动，坚决地遵守上级的一切政策和法令。","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68fceda7c2"},{"id":"8fd7f406e0","type":"paragraph","text":" 李凤英66年7.23","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68fceda7c2"}],"page":{"id":"07253f9dcd","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68fceda7c2","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}